Hello everyone! I need help to build and deploy my UI extension.
The build of December 12 was done successfully.
Since two days ago I've been trying to do a new release (in which I actually simply added a new serverless function without any changes to the dependencies) and I get the following error.

[/app/app.functions/package-lock.json] Couldn't build serverless package because there's a problem in `package.json`. Run `npm install` under `package.json` and try again. Details: `<http://java.net|java.net>.SocketTimeoutException: Read timed out`.

Local development proceeds correctly without problems so I suspect the problem is with the platform.

Anyone have any ideas?

Platform Version: 2023.2

